{"TopicId":189388,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"Deploy solar panels with one button, this exists?","CreatedByName":"Fierce Wolf","CreatedById":200019,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-29T18:00:32Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Fierce Wolf","CreatedById":200019,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-29T18:00:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHello everyone,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI want/need/ohyesplease a button (beside the lights or landing action group for best) to auto deploy all available and non-shrouded solar panels.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs there a mod for this? Couldn\u0027t find any.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks a lot!! \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPd: Antennas would be nice too.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HebaruSan","CreatedById":156657,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-29T18:25:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think that\u0027s this:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022129964\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed7545575671\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/155858-18x-all-yall-continued-one-button-common-action-grouping/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:211px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"zer0Kerbal","CreatedById":190933,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-29T20:36:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nmechjeb also has it - under utilities - and others. so does SM.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"jimmymcgoochie","CreatedById":199902,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-30T17:41:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUm... Put them in an action group? You can assign them in edit mode, or in v1.8 anywhere at all, and just press the button you assign to deploy them. It\u0027s entirely do-able with the stock game, I don\u0027t see why you need a mod for it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DStaal","CreatedById":155685,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-30T19:13:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223697411\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022189388\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221572457272\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022199902\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022jimmymcgoochie\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, jimmymcgoochie said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUm... Put them in an action group? You can assign them in edit mode, or in v1.8 anywhere at all, and just press the button you assign to deploy them. It\u0027s entirely do-able with the stock game, I don\u0027t see why you need a mod for it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBecause it\u0027s far easier to use the mod than to spend several minutes every time you build a ship?\u00A0 Because action groups are limited and you may want them for something else?\u00A0 Because sometimes you forget?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"jimmymcgoochie","CreatedById":199902,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-01T16:32:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223697459\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022189388\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221572462837\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022155685\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022DStaal\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 10/30/2019 at 7:13 PM, DStaal said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBecause it\u0027s far easier to use the mod than to spend several minutes every time you build a ship?\u00A0 Because action groups are limited and you may want them for something else?\u00A0 Because sometimes you forget?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBecause 30 seconds of clicking is too much effort? Because over 20 different action groups to pick from (including\u00A0gear/lights/brakes/abort and various control groups e.g. for powered wheels) isn\u0027t enough? Because you can now add, edit and remove action groups whenever you like?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-01T16:58:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223697459\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022189388\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221572462837\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022155685\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022DStaal\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 10/30/2019 at 3:13 PM, DStaal said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBecause sometimes you forget?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you\u0027re using 1.8 or higher this is no longer a valid argument, as in 1.8 you can now edit action groups in flight.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI still use All Y\u0027All, myself.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RW-1","CreatedById":107278,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-01T19:55:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nASET IVA has a toggle that will do this ...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"zer0Kerbal","CreatedById":190933,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-01T21:07:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022129964\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed5695320522\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/151340-12-smart-parts-continued/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:214px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022143330\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed2379861129\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/150666-*/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:214px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-11-01T21:08:22Z\u0022 title=\u002211/01/2019 09:08  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003ENovember 1, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by zer0Kerbal\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Teilnehmer","CreatedById":143330,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-11-02T06:03:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223698548\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022189388\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221572642428\u0022 